#

Seared Tuna with Avocado Salsa

16 min
$15
300 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

fish

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

quickhealthydinner

Description

A quick and flavorful dish featuring perfectly seared tuna paired with a refreshing avocado salsa.

Ingredients

  • tuna steaks: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • tomato: 1 medium
  • red onion: 1/4 small
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cayenne pepper: a pinch
